-- MOVES-Lombard Odier names head of European private client business
-- 
-- Tue Jul 15, 2014 07:19AM EDT
-- None



July 15 (Reuters) - Swiss private bank Lombard Odier said it appointed Henry Fischel-Bock as head of its European private client business, effective Jan. 1.

Fischel-Bock joins Lombard Odier from Barclays Wealth where he led the UK and European wealth management business, Lombard said.